snippet.title: RWBY: Grimm Eclipse - Definitive Edition - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Huntsmen and Huntresses, are you ready for some intense hack n slash action?

The definitive RWBY experience available now on Nintendo Switch - including over two years of content updates and DLC, eight new outfits, and two-player couch co-op.

Grab RWBY: Grimm Eclipse Definitive Edition today!
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/rwby-grimm-eclipse-definitive-edition-switch/
